resources.name: token-get
resources.description:
Pogi Authetication/Login operation

## Parameters
* userId: The user's id/email address
* password: The password

## Response
* Success: returns a token
* Failure: error, and message

### Please set the following Environment Variables
* userId ({{ _.userId }})
* password ({{ _.password }})

resources.name: token-invalidate
resources.description:
Pogi Logout/Token Invalidate operation

## Parameter
* token - can be passed in cookies, or in the json payload
